  "title": "Steel structure Drafter",
  "description": "<p>1. Creates drawings based on client’s requirements and specifications.</p><p>2. Amends and updates drawings as and when corrections are made as directed by superiors.</p><p>3. Co-ordinated with site staff, contractor, and project team on the drawings and to ensure works are within schedule.</p><p>4. Conducts regular reviews and ensures that the preparation/finalisation of drawings are compliant with various statutory guidelines.</p><p>5. Requirement from Diploma to Degree of Civil Engineering to consider only.</p><p>5a. For Diploma / Degree candidate a must to operate Tekla modelling / Revit / Autocad.</p>",
